examples.en: How much do you think it will cost, approximately?
Can you give me the approximate cost of the repair?
There are approximately 8,000 species of ants.
The journey time to London is approximately four hours.
The plane will be landing in approximately 20 minutes.
This is the approximate location of the ancient city.
The company grosses approximately $80 million a year.
There are approximately 336 dimples on a golf ball.
The colors in the pictures can only approximate the real thing.
All of the planets rotate the sun in approximately the same ecliptic.
The human genome contains approximately three billion chemical base pairs.
It contains approximately a third of the minimum daily requirement.
The space shuttle can carry a maximum payload of approximately 50,000 pounds.
Officials at the school say they received a bomb threat at approximately 11:30 a.m. today.
People come and go, but the population of this town has remained approximately constant for the past decade.
I've finally found a vegetarian burger that approximates the taste of real beef.
10,000 men had volunteered by the end of September; thereafter, approximately 1,000 men enlisted each month.
